  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb4\u0b95 \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0b89\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1!",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Jaffna University Media Department Head promoted to Professor!",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Head of the Department of Media Studies, University of Jaffna and Senior Lecturer, Dr.C. Raghuram has been promoted to professor. The approval was given by the University Council today (25).",
        "The Monthly Meeting of the University Council was held on Saturday morning under the chairmanship of Associate Professor C. Sirisarkunaraja.",
        "University Grants Commission Circulars The evaluation report of the industry experts who evaluated Raghuram's application and the results of the interview were presented at today's meeting.",
        "Based on them, Dr. C., Head of the Department of Media Studies and Senior Lecturer of the Faculty of Arts. Raghuram has been promoted to Professor in Media Studies."
      ],
